<!-- Background Colors
Dark Background: bg-gray-900 (for main backgrounds)
or
Dark Background: bg-gradient-to-r from-slate-700 to-zinc-800 (for main backgrounds)

Card Background: bg-gray-800 (for cards and containers)
or
Card Background: bg-gradient-to-r from-slate-600 to-zinc-700 (for cards and containers)

Navbar Background: bg-gray-700 (for the navbar)
or
Navbar Background: bg-gradient-to-r from-slate-500 to-zinc-600 (for the navbar)

Text Colors
Primary Text: text-white (for main text)
Secondary Text: text-gray-300 (for subtext and less important information)
Placeholder Text: placeholder-gray-500 (for input placeholders)

Button Colors
Primary Button Background: bg-blue-600 (for primary actions)
Primary Button Hover: hover:bg-blue-500 (for hover effect)
Secondary Button Background: bg-yellow-500 (for secondary actions)
Secondary Button Hover: hover:bg-yellow-400 (for hover effect)
Danger/Error Background: bg-red-600 (for error messages)
Danger/Error Hover: hover:bg-red-500 (for hover effect)

Border Colors

Input Border: border-gray-600 (for input fields)
Card Border: border-gray-700 (for card borders) -->